# Internal Policies Reference

Before development changes, review the internal policies wiki index:

`C:\Users\cpatino\OneDrive - Compañía Panameña de Aviación, S.A\General - Digital Marketing\📜 Policies\wiki\index.md`

Applicable notes for this repository:

- Do not expose, commit, print, or document secrets from `.env`, Doppler, CMS tokens, database URLs, Redis credentials, API keys, or analytics credentials.
- Escalate for review if a change introduces new vendor services, paid tools, contracts, PII exchange, PCI exposure, or new external data processors.
- Treat reservation, traveler, consent, QR access log, IP hash, and user agent data as sensitive operational data.
- Prefer local validation with existing project scripts before proposing deployment.
- Do not run build/compile commands to discover errors in this project; builds are slow. Use the local dev server for validation, and rely on user-provided build errors when compilation fails in CI/deploy.
